                <p>Filipino crypto users benefit from their country’s mandatory laws.</p>
                <h2 class="ph-headline ph-headline-f8789bc1 ph-headline-text"><strong>US Compliance</strong></h2>
                <p>You confirm you’re not in a US-embargoed country or on restricted lists for crypto investing.</p>
