        'index_overview_title' => 'Floventra Crypto Overview',
        'index_overview_text' => '<p>As cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum transform global finance, Floventra connects investors with trusted brokers to seize these opportunities. Here’s a detailed look at our platform’s strengths and limitations for your crypto journey.</p>
