                <p><strong>Application Type: </strong>Cryptocurrency Investment Tool</p>',
        'index_rating' => 'Editor’s Score:',
        'index_pros' => '<h4>Advantages</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Trusted Crypto Brokers: Connects you to ASIC-compliant brokers offering Bitcoin, Ethereum, and more.</li>
                    <li>Free Platform: No fees, funded by broker partnerships.</li>
