                <p>Choose between manual investing or AI automation to match your experience and time, with support for multiple accounts to refine your crypto strategies and boost profits.</p>',
        'about_test' => 'TRY Floventra FOR CRYPTO',
        'about_software' => '<h3 class="au-headline au-headline-e3bc14d6 au-headline-text">
                        <strong>Our Crypto Mission</strong></h3>
                    <p>Floventra is designed as an intuitive tool for crypto investors, enabling effortless investing in Bitcoin, Ethereum, and altcoins without prior experience.</p>
