        'contact_form' => 'Get in Touch & Start Crypto Investing Free',
        'contact_guide' => '<h2 class="au-headline au-headline-cffb62a7 au-headline-text">Floventra Contact Guidelines</h2>
                <p class="has-global-color-9-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size"><strong>Review these instructions to direct your crypto inquiry to the right team.</strong></p>
                <p class="has-base-3-color has-text-color">For help with registration, crypto investment questions, or technical issues, use the form below, and our support team will respond quickly.</p>',
        // Privacy Page
        'privacy_title' => 'Floventra Privacy Policy - Australian Crypto Data Protection',
        'privacy_desc_content' => 'Learn how Floventra protects your data for secure crypto investing in Australia. Last updated: February 23, <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear() - 2)</script>.',
        'privacy_keywords' => 'privacy policy, Floventra, Australia, crypto data protection, Bitcoin, Ethereum, AI-driven investing',
        'privacy_content' => '<div class="au-container au-container-4160cb6f">
                <p>Last updated: February 23, <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear() - 2)</script></p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Who We Are</h2>
                <p>Our website: <a href="/au/">https://floventra.org/au/</a>.</p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Comments</h2>
                <p>When you leave comments, we collect form data, your IP address, and browser details to protect against spam in our crypto community.</p>
                <p>An anonymized email hash may be sent to Gravatar to check usage. Their privacy policy: https://automattic.com/privacy/. Approved comments display your profile picture publicly.</p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Media</h2>
                <p>Avoid uploading images with EXIF GPS data, as others can extract location details, potentially compromising your crypto investment privacy.</p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Cookies</h2>
                <p>Commenting saves your name, email, and website in cookies for one year for convenience in our crypto platform interactions.</p>
                <p>Visiting our login page sets a temporary cookie to check browser support, deleted when you close your browser, ensuring secure crypto access.</p>
                <p>Logging in saves login and display cookies for two days or a year. Selecting “Remember Me” extends login to two weeks for easier crypto investing. Logging out clears cookies.</p>
                <p>Editing or publishing articles saves a one-day cookie with the post ID, containing no personal data, for seamless platform use.</p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Embedded Content</h2>
                <p>Articles may include embedded content (e.g., crypto market videos or charts) that may collect data or track interactions as if you visited the external site.</p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Data Sharing</h2>
                <p>Password reset emails include your IP address to secure your crypto account.</p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Data Retention</h2>
                <p>Comments and metadata are kept indefinitely for auto-approval, enhancing your experience in our crypto community.</p>
                <p>Registered users’ profile data is stored, editable, or deletable (except usernames). Admins can view/edit it to support your crypto journey.</p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Your Data Rights</h2>
                <p>Request an export or deletion of your data, excluding what we must keep for legal or security purposes related to crypto investing.</p>
                <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-global-color-9-color has-text-color">Where Data Goes</h2>
                <p>Comments may be screened by automated spam detection to protect our crypto platform.</p>
            </div>',
        // Terms Page
        'terms_title' => 'Floventra Terms - Australian Crypto Investment Services',
        'terms_desc_content' => 'Review Floventra’s terms for secure crypto investing in Australia. Last updated: February 23, <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear() - 2)</script>.',
        'terms_keywords' => 'terms and conditions, Floventra, Australia, crypto investment services, Bitcoin, Ethereum, AI-driven investing',
        'terms_content' => '<div class="au-container au-container-d253b3f9">
                <p>Last updated: February 23, <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear() - 2)</script></p>
                <p>Review these terms carefully before using our cryptocurrency investment platform.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-0a80bcf6 au-headline-text"><strong>Key Definitions</strong></h2>
                <p><strong>Interpretation</strong></p>
                <p>Capitalized terms apply in singular or plural for our crypto services.</p>
                <p><strong>Definitions</strong></p>
                <p>For these Terms and Conditions:</p>
                <p>Affiliate: Entity with 50%+ voting share ownership.</p>
                <p>Account: Your unique access to our crypto platform.</p>
                <p>Country: Australia.</p>
                <p>Company: Floventra (“We,” “Us,” “Our”).</p>
                <p>Device: Computer, phone, or tablet accessing our crypto services.</p>
                <p>Service: Our website for crypto investing.</p>
                <p>Terms and Conditions: Agreement governing your use of our crypto platform.</p>
                <p>Third-party Social Media: External content or services in our platform.</p>
                <p>Website: Floventra at <a data-id="9" data-type="page" href="/au/">this address</a>.</p>
                <p>You: The user or entity accessing our crypto services.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-a42ca7f0 au-headline-text"><strong>Agreement</strong></h2>
                <p>These terms govern your use of our crypto platform, outlining your rights and responsibilities for Bitcoin and altcoin investing.</p>
                <p>Access requires agreeing to these terms, applicable to all crypto users.</p>
                <p>If you disagree, do not use our crypto services.</p>
                <p>You must be over 18 to use our platform for crypto investing.</p>
                <p>Our <a href="/au/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> details data collection and protection for crypto users.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-cd0291ec au-headline-text"><strong>Your Crypto Account</strong></h2>
                <p>Provide accurate, current information when signing up for crypto investing. Inaccuracies may lead to account termination.</p>
                <p>Secure your password and report any unauthorized use immediately to protect your crypto investments.</p>
                <p>Usernames must not violate others’ rights or be offensive on our crypto platform.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-c94b9783 au-headline-text"><strong>Intellectual Property</strong></h2>
                <p>Our platform’s content and features (excluding user content) are owned by Floventra and protected by copyright and trademark laws.</p>
                <p>Our trademarks require written consent for use in crypto-related contexts.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-d5986601 au-headline-text"><strong>Third-Party Links</strong></h2>
                <p>We’re not responsible for third-party websites or services linked on our crypto platform, such as external market data providers.</p>
                <p>Review their terms and privacy policies before use to ensure safe crypto investing.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-2bafff1f au-headline-text"><strong>Termination</strong></h2>
                <p>We may suspend or terminate your account for any reason, including term violations, to protect our crypto platform.</p>
                <p>You can stop using our services to end your crypto account.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-ec9ba944 au-headline-text"><strong>Liability Limits</strong></h2>
                <p>Our liability is limited to what you paid or A$150 if no payment was made for crypto services.</p>
                <p>We’re not liable for indirect damages like lost crypto profits, even if advised of risks.</p>
                <p>Some jurisdictions may limit these exclusions, applying maximum enforceable limits.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-a3fc31fb au-headline-text"><strong>“As Is” Disclaimer</strong></h2>
                <p>Our crypto platform is provided “as is” without warranties for performance, accuracy, or error-free operation.</p>
                <p>We do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free crypto investing or data accuracy.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-883daea2 au-headline-text"><strong>Governing Law</strong></h2>
                <p>Australian law governs these terms for crypto services, subject to local or international regulations.</p>
                <p><strong>Dispute Resolution</strong></p>
                <p>Contact us first to resolve crypto-related disputes informally.</p>
                <p><strong>Australian Users</strong></p>
                <p>Australian crypto users benefit from their country’s mandatory laws.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-f8789bc1 au-headline-text"><strong>US Compliance</strong></h2>
                <p>You confirm you’re not in a US-embargoed country or on restricted lists for crypto investing.</p>
                <p><strong>Severability</strong></p>
                <p>Invalid terms will be adjusted; others remain effective for our crypto platform.</p>
                <p><strong>Waiver</strong></p>
                <p>Not enforcing a right doesn’t waive it for future crypto-related actions.</p>
                <p><strong>Translation</strong></p>
                <p>English terms prevail in crypto-related disputes.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-d8a8b7e5 au-headline-text"><strong>Term Changes</strong></h2>
                <p>We may update these terms, with 30 days’ notice for major changes to our crypto services.</p>
                <p>Continued use means you accept updated terms for crypto investing.</p>
                <h2 class="au-headline au-headline-5fe35776 au-headline-text"><strong>Contact Us</strong></h2>
                <p>For questions about these terms, contact us:</p>
                <p>By email: <a href="mailto:info@floventra.org">info@floventra.org</a></p>
                <p>Via our <a data-id="42" data-type="page" href="/au/contact">Contact Us</a> page.</p>
            </div>'
    ],

